## Error handling

### HttpError

```ts
import { HttpError } from "../lib/http";

try {
  await someApiCall();
} catch (err) {
  if (err instanceof HttpError) {
    toast.error(err.error.message);   // Vietnamese message from API
  }
}
```

### In mutations (TanStack Query)

```tsx
useMutation({
  mutationFn: ...,
  onError: (err) => {
    const msg = err instanceof HttpError
      ? err.error.message
      : "Đã có lỗi xảy ra. Vui lòng thử lại.";
    // show toast / set error state
  },
});
```

