## Auth & session

```ts
import { useAuth } from "../hooks/useAuth";

const { isAuthenticated, login, logout } = useAuth();
```

`isAuthenticated` is derived from the access token + Redis session check.
Access token: in-memory only (not localStorage). Refresh token: `localStorage("refresh_token")`.
The `erpApi` client reads the token via `getAccessToken()` automatically.

---

## OpenAPI client regeneration

After adding/changing API endpoints:
```bash
# API must be running on :4000
pnpm openapi:generate
# Commit the updated openapi.snapshot.json
```

The generated types are in `packages/api-client/src/generated/schema.ts`.
Never hand-edit that file.
